Package edu.wisc.game.sql

Class MlcEntry

java.lang.Object
edu.wisc.game.sql.MlcEntry
@Entity
public class MlcEntry
extends Object
An MlcEntry contains the data for a (participant, ruleset, run) tuple. The data is condensed from the appropriate lines of CSV file submitted by an MLC participant.
